{"type": "article", "id": 29216, "title": "办公隔板", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-06T22:51:51Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160706163655J2AeOtF16og7xpHj.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>开放式的工作环境有时会让人无法保持专注的状态工作，也很难有效地保护隐私。<a href=\"http://www.ivankasner.nl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ivan Kasner</a> 和 <a href=\"http://www.ulibudde.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Uli Budde</a> 为荷兰家具公司 <a href=\"http://www.devorm.nl/home\" rel=\"nofollow\">De Vorm</a> 设计了一块带灯饰的隔板 <a href=\"http://www.devorm.nl/products/ak-2-pet-felt-workspace-divider-lamp\" rel=\"nofollow\">AK 2</a>，两边分别装有 LED 灯，可以同时为两边的使用者提供稳定的照明。AK 2 所使用的毛毡由回收的 PET 瓶制作而成的，不仅质地柔软，对声音也有极强的吸附性，一定程度上可以减轻噪音干扰。AK 2 提供多种颜色选择，你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.devorm.nl/contact\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>与 De Vorm 联系购买。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706170410rkT9U0xbwPiAo36u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.580685\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706170410Z2eLzlHX849xVkIc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706170410V8zKDvswXrnpm3iR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.622249\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706170411ZvWFA7oKHLscf8zp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.248470\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}